{"tid":2192414,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明知發燒照驗毒 男子證中招","createTime":"2020-09-07T05:55:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T07:10:09.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"612631b6d8fb07ee63740b28a728b4b6f46bdc52","tid":2192414,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200906/CHQGUL2FI5AHPBC4ZGZAJJYJVY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200906%2FCHQGUL2FI5AHPBC4ZGZAJJYJVY%2F&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp%2FGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=431ff97d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200906%2FCHQGUL2FI5AHPBC4ZGZAJJYJVY%2F&h=9be5d756\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200906/CHQGUL2FI5AHPBC4ZGZAJJYJVY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n明知發燒照驗毒 男子證中招<br />\n<br />\n■昨日新增兩宗經檢測確診的個案，其中一宗來自元朗趙聿修紀念中學的檢測中心。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】為響應特首林鄭月娥號召全民檢測，一名旺角街坊明知有武漢肺炎病徵，仍往檢測中心接受採樣，結果證實確診。全民檢測再驗出兩宗新確診，另一患者是居於元朗的菲傭，無病徵屬隱形患者，逢周末及周日都會與其他外傭聚會，其僱主及幾名外傭朋友均需隔離檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：在囚男子染疫 港首宗  荔枝角收押所及小欖700人需驗武肺<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君昨公佈，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n菲傭陽性 檢測中心照開放<br />\n<br />\n患者9月1日檢測，但過了四天到昨天才確診，是否全民檢測的化驗延誤？張竹君指患者9月3日已驗出初步呈陽性，9月4日已確診及送往檢疫中心，只是公佈時間滯後一天。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：檢疫漏洞 孕婦產檢揭感染<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張表示，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n全民檢測至。。。。。。"},{"pid":"bc66db6249cf29ae30ad52bcd2a6c9e3b27e42d7","tid":2192414,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:08:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁識玩"},{"pid":"3a0cb426739d03205fdfbb1f9f03a3fe357b8885","tid":2192414,"uid":179837,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:09:54.000Z","msg":"冇事使乜去驗<img src=\"